    {
      "_id": 11302,
      "id": "countermeasure_lumis_battle_cry",
      "name": "Countermeasure: Lumi's Battle Cry!",
      "description": "Adventure with Lumi! Depending on how you Tap, Lumi attacks in different forms.<br/><br/><span style=\"color:#FFD780FF\">Tap</span><br/>Lumi strikes in a <color=#FFD780FF><b>Super Power Form</b></color>, attacking nearby enemies continuously, dealing <span style=\"color:#FFE699FF\">AoE Geo DMG</span>. If there are Moondrifts nearby, Lumi will also deal <span style=\"color:#FFE699FF\">AoE Geo DMG</span> to nearby enemies, which will be considered Lunar-Crystallize Reaction DMG.<br/><br/><span style=\"color:#FFD780FF\">Continuous Tapping</span><br/>Time to show what we're really capable of! After using her Elemental Skill, Linnea will feed Lumi sparkling gemstones when her Elemental Skill or Normal Attack is Tapped repeatedly. A full-bellied Lumi will strike in her <color=#FFD780FF><b>Ultimate Power Form</b></color>, dealing an especially powerful instance of <span style=\"color:#FFE699FF\">AoE Geo DMG</span> that is considered Lunar-Crystallize Reaction DMG, switching to <color=#FFD780FF><b>Standard Power Form</b></color>.<br/>Additionally, tapping the Elemental Skill increases Linnea's interruption resistance.",
      "info": "\"You're up, Lumi!\"",
